This is the parts list for the gloves. This list will include the links as well. 

1st: Conductive Nylon Fabric Tape
Link(s): https://www.adafruit.com/product/3961 

2nd: Motherboard (ESP32-wroom-32)
Link(s): https://www.amazon.com/KeeYees-Development-Bluetooth-Microcontroller-ESP-WROOM-32/dp/B07QCP2451/ref=sr_1_6?crid=34BEH972Z8649&keywords=esp32-wroom-32&qid=1644360747&sprefix=esp32-wroom%2Caps%2C152&sr=8-6

3rd: Conductive Thread (Yarn)
Links(s): https://www.adafruit.com/product/603

4rd: Velostat
Link(s): https://tinkersphere.com/conductive-thread-fabric/1454-velostat-pressure-sensitive-conductive-sheet.html

5th (Optional): Flex Sensor Guide (Needs To Be 3D Printing Or Maded, Like From Cardboard)
Link(s): https://github.com/TwidgeVR/bend_sensor_guide_node/blob/main/Flex%20Sensor%20Guide%20v2.stl
